{"about_the_game":"This is a military-themed single-player shooting game produced by individual developers. In the game, you will play the role of a commander, drive a tank and command your companions, search for and assassinate the enemy's field commander in the wilderness.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Forming A Team</h2>As a commander, you can configure your armored units in the garage<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/Garage.gif?t=1694865846\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Charging</h2>You need drive the currently selected equipment with the keyboard and mouse.<br>As a commander, you can give orders to your partner vehicle, mark the march or fire the target<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/\u6587\u6848_\u534f\u540c\u4f5c\u6218.gif?t=1694865846\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Covert Assassination</h2>The battlefield is full of enemy scouts, don't be spotted by them, otherwise more armored troops will come to support.<br>Long-distance covert assassination is a good option<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/\u6587\u6848_\u8fdc\u7a0b\u72d9\u51fb2.gif?t=1694865846\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Reconnaissance and Beyond Visual Range Strike</h2>A good commander will reasonably allocate the roles of the convoy<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Helicopters and wheeled vehicles have powerful maneuverability to penetrate behind enemy lines and discover key targets.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/Search.gif?t=1694865846\" /><br><br></li><li>Mark targets and conduct long-range precision strikes<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/Attack.gif?t=1694865846\" /></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Be Careful</h2>The enemy is ambus